What you need to know:

AFC Leopards have never had more than one honorary patron as was reported in a section of the media last weekHe took over from Nairobi Senator Johnson Sakaja last year, and has been supporting the club since the withdrawal of betting firm SportPesa following a tax dispute with the governmentMudavadi, a long-time supporter of the club, has the capacity to pull in resources even from the highest office in the land